A body blessed by the gods..... or just a lucky lady

descriptionHtml:
[center]﻿[/center][center][color=#6d9eeb][b][size=6]Overview[/size].[/b][/color][/center][size=4]
[list]
[*][size=4][i][color=#ffd966]This is a [/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]UUNP[/b][/color][color=#ffd966]/[/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]CBBE [/b][/color][color=#ffd966]Preset for [/color][b][color=#6fa8dc]BodySlide.[/color][/b][/i][/size]
[/list][color=#ffd966][i]
[/i][/color][list]
[*][i][color=#ffd966]The Preset focuses on a [/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]heavy,[/b][/color][color=#ffd966] [/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]supported[/b][/color][color=#ffd966], and [/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]rounded top[/b][/color][color=#ffd966], while giving a [/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]curvy eye[/b][/color][color=#ffd966] - [/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]candy[/b][/color][color=#ffd966] bottom.[/color][/i]
[/list][color=#ffd966][i]
[/i][/color][list]
[*][i][color=#ffd966]This preset is inspired from some top heavy [/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]Anime Characters[/b][/color][color=#ffd966] and recreated to my best ability.[/color][/i]
[/list][color=#ffd966][i]
[/i][/color][list]
[*][i][color=#ffd966]The Body naturally scales down from 100-0 weight ([/color][color=#6fa8dc][b]Busty to Skinny-ish[/b][/color][color=#ffd966]) See pictures for reference.[/color][/i]
[/list][color=#ffd966][i]
[/i][/color][list]
[*][i][color=#ffd966]Hope you enjoy.[/color] [b][color=#6fa8dc]Cheers!! ( [/color][color=#38761d][u]Endorse if you like it[/u][/color][color=#6fa8dc]) [/color][/b][/i]
[/list][/size]
